---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Free Scan"
  description="See what we'd find on your site. Enter your URL and get a preview of our structural audit — top findings, prioritized by severity."
  noindex
>
  <Section class="pt-28 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="mb-4">See what we'd find.</h1>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-xl leading-relaxed mb-12">
        Enter your URL and we'll run a structural scan powered by Muttr. You'll
        get a preview of your top findings &mdash; each tagged with severity,
        root cause cluster, and confidence tier.
      </p>

      <!-- V1: Netlify Forms. Submission lands in Netlify dashboard; async scan -->
      <!-- pipeline (Muttr) is triggered manually from there until Phase 3. -->
      <form
        name="scan"
        method="POST"
        action="/thanks?type=scan"
        data-netlify="true"
        netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
        class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-lg mx-auto"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="scan" />
        <p class="hidden">
          <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
        </p>
        <div>
          <label for="scan-url" class="block text-sm font-medium text-primary-text mb-2">Website URL</label>
          <input
            type="url"
            id="scan-url"
            name="url"
            required
            class="w-full bg-bg-inset border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-primary-text placeholder:text-secondary-text/50 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors"
            placeholder="https://yoursite.com"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="scan-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-primary-text mb-2">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="scan-email"
            name="email"
            required
            class="w-full bg-bg-inset border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-primary-text placeholder:text-secondary-text/50 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors"
            placeholder="you@company.com"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="scan-company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-primary-text mb-2">Company <span class="text-secondary-text">(optional)</span></label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="scan-company"
            name="company"
            class="w-full bg-bg-inset border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-primary-text placeholder:text-secondary-text/50 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors"
            placeholder="Company name"
          />
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="bg-accent text-on-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors w-full"
        >
          Scan My Site
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-secondary-text text-sm">
        <span>No credit card required</span>
        <span>&bull;</span>
        <span>Results in 24-48 hours</span>
        <span>&bull;</span>
        <span>Top 5-10 findings</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <Section elevated>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-8">What's in a scan</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-accent mb-2">Top findings by severity</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-text">The 5-10 most impactful structural issues on your site, each with severity rating and confidence tier (confirmed / probable / hypothesis).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-accent mb-2">Root cause clusters</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-text">Findings grouped by their underlying pattern &mdash; not 47 disconnected issues, but the 3-5 systemic causes producing them. Fix the cluster, not the symptoms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-accent mb-2">The full picture preview</h4>
          <p class="text-secondary-text">A count of all detected issues beyond the top findings. "We found N additional issues across X categories" &mdash; explored in the full Platform Technical Audit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Want the full audit?</h2>
      <p class="text-secondary-text text-lg mb-8">
        The scan is a preview. The Get Right is the full engagement &mdash; three
        simultaneous audits, one unified roadmap, 90 days of founder-level support.
      </p>
      <a href="/the-get-right" class="text-accent font-medium hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors">
        Learn about The Get Right &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
